method 1)
---------
1) copy code in remix ide 
2) select JavaScript VM
3) compile and deploy

method 2) to deploy on rinkeby test network
-------------------------------------------
1) copy paste code on remix ide
2) select environment injected web3
3) open metamask. select the rinkiby test network.
4) compile and deploy the contract

method 3) to deploy on rinkeby test network
-------------------------------------------
1) copy paste the contract on remix IDE
2) login on https://www.myetherwallet.com/ and connect to wallet with metamask
3) you can deploy contract directly with the help of byte code that you can copy from remix ide after compilation
4 )when you paste the bytecode. delete everything but object value
5) copy token addrress from etherscan 


method 4)
-----------
1) go to https://wallet.ethereum.org/contracts
2) add tokens here with the help of token(contract) address on etherscan
